Enum EjbcaServiceTypes

    public enum EjbcaServiceTypes
extends java.lang.Enum<EjbcaServiceTypes>
implements org.cesecore.audit.enums.ServiceType
    EJBCA specific security audit event service type, for audit using CESecore's audit log. When doing secure audit log ServiceType is used to indicate if the log was executed from the core itself or by an external application. In relation to CESeCore, EJBCA acts as an "external application" in this case.
    See Also:
    ServiceTypes, EjbcaEventTypes, EjbcaModuleTypes
